{"about_the_game":"In COLORFUL GHOSTS, you'll face mind-bending challenges! Ghosts of different sizes are hungry for candies. These candies make them change color and blend with other little ghosts! Find the right combination between the ghost and the candy to complete the challenge.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976190/extras/copy_puzzle.png?t=1723166033\" /><br><br><br>Oops, it's not that easy! Ghosts can be stopped by blocks, doors, and holes! Find a way to use these objects to your advantage.<br><br>Is there a hole in your way? Find the <strong>right button</strong> to close it.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976190/extras/gif_botao_ponte.gif?t=1723166033\" /><br><br>Push the blocks with the ghost's head. And remember that you can press a button with the block!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976190/extras/gif_empurrando_caixa__1_.gif?t=1723166033\" /><br><br>To open a door, find the <strong>right key</strong>!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976190/extras/gif_chave.gif?t=1723166033\" /><br><br>Struggling with colors? Don't worry, Colorful Ghosts features an accessibility system, <strong>ColorAdd</strong>. The symbols appearing on the ghosts, candies, and final goals will help you identify which color is there!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976190/extras/copy_coloradd_2_menor.png?t=1723166033\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976190/extras/copy_topo.png?t=1723166033\" /><br><br><strong>Coming soon a new world for you to play!</strong>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2976190?t=172316